node.text: I can’t believe I had my blessing three months ago! Time flies by so fast. Carrying a baby for 9 months comes with a lot but it was the best feeling ever. Knowing that you have a baby in your stomach & feeling all the little movements was the best feeling ever. Sometimes I wish he was still in my stomach so I can protect him from the outside world but I’m so glad I forever have the loml , my soulmate & my bestfriend for the rest of my life ❤️ mommy loves you ressiah!

node.text:
To my son ,
Thank you for changing my life. I finally developed a love that is so unconditional. I promise to protect you & I promise to give you the world because you deserve it 💙 love you forever ! 05/03/21 👶🏽

node.text: I’ve been waiting my 9 months to meet you little one. This journey hasn’t been easy, especially what’s still ahead of us, but knowing we get to meet you at the other end of it makes it all worth it 👶🏽✨ 05/08 (stay tuned for these pictures 🤞🏽)
